<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #4F46E5;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-top: none;
        border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4F46E5;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to GO3!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for joining GO3! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
      <p>Your account has been successfully created using <%= @user.provider&.capitalize || 'social' %> authentication.</p>
      <p>You can now access all the features of our platform:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Manage your personal information</li>
        <li>Securely access your data</li>
        <li>Collaborate with your team</li>
        <li>And much more!</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To sign in to your account, simply click the button below:</p>
      <p>
        <a href="<%= @url %>" class="button">Sign In</a>
      </p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>
        The GO3 Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to <%= @user.email %>. If you didn't create an account, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
